changes from 0.5.1 to 0.6.0:

2004-04-26

	* Changed: Moved logic for window and
		applet into one class.

2004-01-08 Rds <rds@rdsarts.com>

	* Fixed: Options.xml fixed. ;) Widget layout also
		cleaned up. Should work much better when using
		text-under-graph mode.

2004-01-07 Rds <rds@rdsarts.com>

	* Fixed: Logic in lifetime display code.
	* Fixed: Fonts. They now look spiffy. :)
		Still need to fix the Options.xml file, though.

2004-01-03 Rds <rds@rdsarts.com>

	* Added: Options for displaying text/bar. Now, instead of
		one hard to figure out line, it's 4. ;)
	* BROKE: font handling of text. This is broke until I get
		the new style code in. =\

2003-12-15 Rds <rds@rdsarts.com>

	* fixed: Changed labels in Options.xml to reflect
		how time-till-update works now.


changes from 0.5.0 to 0.5.1:

2003-12-14 Tilo Riemer <riemer@lincvs.org>

	* adapted for acpi.py 0.3.0
	Baroque needs at least acpi.py 0.3.0 now because
	a changed return type of estimated_lifetime
	
2003-12-10 Rds <rds@rdsarts.com>

	* fixed: ACPI freeze when going from charging from
		battery-powered.
	* cleaned up some logic
	* option change: time-till-update now works off
		tenths of a second instead of milliseconds


